text: "Should've Been a Cowboy" is a 1993 debut single by country singer Toby Keith and is the leading single from his debut studio album Toby Keith. It topped the country charts in the United States and Canada. It also made number 93 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart. ==References== Category:1993 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Country songs Category:Toby Keith songs
title: Should've Been a Cowboy
